### 1. Register - Créer un compte
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mlp.ma",
  "password": "admin123",
  "name": "Admin MLP"
}

### 2. Login - Se connecter
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mlp.ma",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 3. Me - Voir mon profil (copie le token du login ici)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer COLLE_TON_TOKEN_ICI

### 4. Logout
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer COLLE_TON_TOKEN_ICI

### 5. Test erreur - mauvais mot de passe
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mlp.ma",
  "password": "mauvais"
}

### 6. Test erreur - sans token
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me